{"tid":791983,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"諗到條發達大計 只限今晚！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2018-08-24T08:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T13:40:16.000Z","uid":9504,"like":20,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"12af325c2f08e0ce5a91218960395475801c8d0b","tid":791983,"uid":9504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T08:30:25.000Z","msg":"今日係農歷七月十四 一定大把人去燒街衣<br />\n而燒街衣既人一定留低好多祭品<br />\n有生果 硬幣 飯 等等...<br />\n試諗下 今晚去執晒佢<br />\n就好似食雞咁 成地都係裝備任你執<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/162946_1c9c276304b214a40c580837285f05e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F162946_1c9c276304b214a40c580837285f05e0.png&h=700d9f9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n硬幣 - 唔洗講 實好多人掉毫子同一蚊 兩蚊銀<br />\n執執埋埋都應該有幾萬至幾千 睇你勤唔勤力<br />\n<br />\n生果 - 執執埋埋 自食又得 儲埋過幾日去賣番比生果檔 我諗幾皮野都走唔甩<br />\n<br />\n飯 - 要生米 熟米唔要 生米執執埋埋 儲夠一袋5KG就去搵間米鋪打包 又一筆<br />\n<br />\n其他祭品 應該會有遮 假屋 衫 果d<br />\n儲儲埋埋 拎去賣 不得了！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位！！執裝喇喂！！！！！"},{"pid":"ccbcfa5b463ee5d64152784ff4d4ce7c20f7a073","tid":791983,"uid":122134,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T08:31:16.000Z","msg":"洗你教?<br />\n今朝已經執緊"},{"pid":"f07f0a7ce522a8277afbf6d4b9df07e518f7e2df","tid":791983,"uid":9504,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ccbcfa5b463ee5d64152784ff4d4ce7c20f7a073","tid":791983,"uid":122134,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T08:31:16.000Z","msg":"洗你教?<br />\n今朝已經執緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T08:31:40.000Z","msg":"仆街 搶閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"